19#include "ODRowReader.h"
20#include "BarcodeFormat.h"
21
22#include <vector>
23#include <memory>
24
25namespace ZXing {
26
27class DecodeHints;
28
29namespace OneD {
30
31class UPCEANReader;
32
33/**
34* <p>A reader that can read all available UPC/EAN formats. If a caller wants to try to
35* read all such formats, it is most efficient to use this implementation rather than invoke
36* individual readers.</p>
37*
38* @author Sean Owen
39*/
40class MultiUPCEANReader : public RowReader
41{
42public:
43 explicit MultiUPCEANReader(const DecodeHints& hints);
44 ~MultiUPCEANReader() override;
45
46 Result decodeRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row, std::unique_ptr<DecodingState>& state) const override;
47
48private:
49 std::vector<std::unique_ptr<const UPCEANReader>> _readers;
50 bool _canReturnUPCA = false;
51};
52
53} // OneD
54} // ZXing
